Syslog Client Logging Framework for Erlang

This software contains code derived from the lager project developed and
maintained by Basho Technologies, Inc. and contributors. The Apache 2.0 license
is applied to the file 'syslog_logger.erl' solely. It is basically a modified
version of the file 'lager_backend_throttle.erl'. The original software is
available from https://github.com/basho/lager.

This software also contains code derived from the sasl_syslog project developed
and maintained by Travelping GmbH and contributors. The original software is
available from https://github.com/travelping/sasl_syslog.
